# PlaceTrack — Complete Project Documentation

> A full-stack Campus Placement Tracking System built as a DBMS Mini Project using MS SQL Server, Node.js, and vanilla HTML/CSS/JS.

---

## 1. What is PlaceTrack?

PlaceTrack is a **web-based placement management portal** with two distinct user roles:

- **Students** — Register, build their academic profile, browse active company drives, check their eligibility, and apply.
- **Admins (Placement Officers)** — Monitor all students, manage company drives, review and update application statuses, and broadcast notifications.

Everything is connected to a **real MS SQL Server database**. No fake data. No local JSON files.

